title: MASH 34pc Studio Pro Makeup Make Up Cosmetic Brush Set Kit w/ Leather Case - For Eye Shadow, Blush, Concealer, Etc.
description: New from MASH! Pick a make up brush set that is right for you.  They include all the brushes you'll ever need to create perfectly polished makeup styles.  Perfect for professional salons or personal use! Each brush is covered with a clear plastic wrap for cleanliness. For best result it is recommended to wash brushes & air dry before use. These affordable makeup brushes sets contains every brush pictured.How to Clean Makeup Brushes:1. Run the bristles of brush under warm running water.2. Apply a small amount of gentle shampoo to bristles and work into a light lather.3. Rinse bristles thoroughly under running water. You will notice that the water leaving the brush is tinted from old makeup.4. Continue rinsing until no color leaves the brush.5. Allow it to air-dry.
